CLIENT AND SERVER MODEL

client : machine or process that request data from servers.
server : machine which provide data to client .

what happens when you search something on internet?

users access website through domain main and connects to DNS service which is third party service which provide ip address of the website that we want to hit .

once we have gotten the ip address , request will be send it server directly and response is returned in the form of HTML pages or json. 

